external_knowledge:
Experienced researchers: those who have completed significant numbers of iterations;
Productive: refers to researchers completing more than ten iterations;
Over five minutes: average execution time greater than 300 seconds.

sql:
SELECT AVG(accuracy) AS Average_Accuracy
FROM model_versions
WHERE version_id = 1;

external_knowledge:
- Wise guardians refer to senior researchers in the metaphorical context;
- Titans symbolize projects with generous budgets;
- Whispers of performance are metaphorical for performance metrics;
- The silent realm alludes to early deployment stages, specifically before deployment ID 1.

sql:
SELECT *
FROM iterations
WHERE jaccard_i > (SELECT AVG(jaccard_i) FROM iterations);

SELECT environment 
FROM model_deployments 
WHERE deployment_id = 0;

SELECT DISTINCT researchers.name
FROM researchers
JOIN iterations ON researchers.researcher_id = iterations.researcher_id;

SELECT *
FROM model_deployments
LEFT JOIN deployment_metrics ON model_deployments.deployment_id = deployment_metrics.deployment_id;

SELECT version_number, accuracy, precision, recall
FROM model_versions
WHERE (accuracy + precision + recall) / 3 > 0.85;

SELECT deployment_id, status
FROM model_deployments
WHERE status = 'live';
